আজো তা'র ফুল কলিদের ঘুম টুটেনি, তন্দ্রাতে বিলোল।

snippet.textDisplay:
Since closeup one, Hrituraj has been one of my favourite singer. Even his brother, Pritwiraj was too (R.I.P). This fusion is topnotch. Hrituraj melted our mind as expected. But Nandita!! Listening her for the first time! Is she even real! Oh my God! Her voice in this song is like two scooped vanilla ice-cream with cherry on top!  

#Bulbuli is love 💚
